    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to the Bread Market Research Questionnaire!</h1>
        <p>We invite you to participate in our exciting bread marketing survey! Your valuable insights will help us understand what types of bread consumers prefer, from whole wheat to gluten-free options. We're curious about your purchasing habits tooâ€”how often do you buy bread, and what factors influence your decisions, like price, freshness, or nutritional content? Your responses will paint a clearer picture of how bread fits into your daily routine. 

Beyond preferences and habits, we want to know your thoughts on bread's healthiness compared to other carbs. </p>
